{"tid":868651,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夜麻麻,得返自己一個果時","createTime":"2018-10-19T15:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T11:26:55.000Z","uid":216800,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7e50b0a15edd6c1caa35428af7b82931566008","tid":868651,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"夜麻麻,得返自己一個<br />\n坐係電腦前,一邊食住杯麵,一邊對住個MON發吽豆<br />\n雖然腦海空白,但心情幾起伏不定<br />\n有種感覺開始湧上心頭,慢慢地 慢慢地<br />\n腦海開始回憶起以前既日子<br />\n回憶往事<br />\n回憶家人<br />\n回憶朋友<br />\n回憶她<br />\n<br />\n依個係一種折磨..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似上北健果首DIARY一樣<br />\n將自己僅有既氣球比左青蛙之後<br />\n在不經意之中,青蛙係度剪自己既手指<br />\n雖然一開始已經知道剪緊,但無諗過青蛙真係會剪落去<br />\n最後手指被剪斷左,徬徨既自己開始奔離此地<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既可以去聽下(3:08開始)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MkrAZi7GMpI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMkrAZi7GMpI&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=eaef5a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MkrAZi7GMpI</a><br />\n<br />\n都幾想好似最後果段咁比核彃炸死之後,<br />\n最後得返個靈魂都可以望佢一眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86703318daf7252bcd7632b5ce5769b7edb43c7a","tid":868651,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"中二病"},{"pid":"c7eea1fcffbc0064b4fd7013e6b6b6c49300f498","tid":868651,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86703318daf7252bcd7632b5ce5769b7edb43c7a","tid":868651,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"中二病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:04:59.000Z","msg":"都幾中二下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466a80f73b4f5abf243b334d2c40a8a5531fec4e","tid":868651,"uid":186765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"雖然腦海空白,但心情幾起伏不定<br />\n有種感覺開始湧上心頭,慢慢地 慢慢地<br /